{"tid":1398413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸網上連儂牆要人！！","createTime":"2019-08-02T19:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T20:25:21.000Z","uid":24280,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d7baa710b8f2e1dfcc09370a0fb6c11dfb57cd","tid":1398413,"uid":24280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:19:21.000Z","msg":"話說有個香港人開咗個ig放哂好多理智嘅大陸人對我地嘅支持<br />\n不惜冒住生命危險去鼓勵我地<br />\n依家己經有91張！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xs9Zib.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xs9Zib.png&h=b66578a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住有條大陸西發哂癲話要將上面啲人搵哂出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yuytvrH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyuytvrH.png&h=e3a36294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eBbVUTr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeBbVUTr.png&h=37185709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（目前照佢咁講佢已經開始搵咗北航同教育部作相關調查上面的學生証教師証同北航研究生証）<br />\n<br />\n佢仲話如果係真嘅話寧願自爆都要搵哂啲人出黎<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGLSW7n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGLSW7n.png&h=2e74e7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好驚條臭西真係會搵到啲人出黎<br />\n到時佢地就好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難得大陸有真正屬於我地嘅同胞 我地要救下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條女極需要捐贈器官有無人幫幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009280c07c7b56c68d03b58713c96aaab8bbfcca","tid":1398413,"uid":24280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:20:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"226993e67012881f35936a0eef99b9e4d29db92c","tid":1398413,"uid":24280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:20:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"09742a1522808d7b50fadcb04a2032ebc6ec0b4e","tid":1398413,"uid":24